{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":66369,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":11309,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"蹲","timestamp":1593505821,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":66372,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":11309,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"以我的多年演讲经验（真的）来看，用大嗓门掩盖紧张感是一个有效办法","timestamp":1593505890,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":66442,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":11309,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"cz跟人说话就会紧张，怕说错话对方在意。后来发现很多时候没人听，就放开了，当然有些时候还是紧张，尤其是那种有记录的场合","timestamp":1593506934,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":66507,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":11309,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 没人听可太真实了","timestamp":1593508145,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":66627,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":11309,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我每次pre的时候都当作聊天就没那么紧张了。以前大一的时候也会很紧张，后来选了美双之后课堂pre是那种很轻松的，甚至pre的人都可以坐下，然后一大帮人侃侃而谈的那种，突然就觉得pre也不过如此，形式制造紧张感…所以之后的pre每次都觉得是聊天，形式就是我需要走的一个过场而已","timestamp":1593510230,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":67660,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":11309,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"当作聊天放松 不是大场合就不紧张了 也许可以线上pre","timestamp":1593527304,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":8,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":11309,"reply":6,"tag":null,"text":"有朋友做pre时候超级紧张总是发抖吗（甚至开班会同学交流发言时间长也紧张），感觉常说的多练习有点像恶性循环...一想到以后还有论文答辩之类的就觉得应该赶紧克服这个问题..或许有人用什么方法解决紧张了吗...","timestamp":1593505681,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782586,"url":"","vote":{}}}